<template>
  <el-form ref="form" :model="form" label-width="80px">
    <el-form-item label="活动名称">
      <el-input v-model="form.name"></el-input>
    </el-form-item>

    <el-form-item>
      <el-button type="primary" @click="submit">重置</el-button>
    </el-form-item>
  </el-form>
</template>
<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      form: {
        name: '',
        region: '',
        date1: '',
        date2: '',
        delivery: false,
        type: [],
        resource: '',
        desc: ''
      }
    }
  },
  methods: {
    onSubmit() {
      console.log('submit!');
    }
  }
}
</script>
